Subject: [PATCH 055/194] hack! ASoC: qdsp6: q6voice-dai: add internal mi2s

The Snapdragon 660 and 670 internal sound card have internal MI2S ports.
Add support for them in q6voice.

Signed-off-by: Richard Acayan <mailingradian@gmail.com>
